_sText: Based on the Wieden+Kennedy headquarters building in Portland Oregon. Map takes place after an unknown natural disaster. Features winding paths through rubble, toxic flood water and a distinct off-grid feel. Illumination is provided mainly though the skylight, casting large shadows across the interior space. Created with Hammer in 3 weeks for Counter-Strike Source GunGame.

gg_victoria_street_beta1

Map Features:
Map Style: 1800 - 1900's London
64 Spawns
Unique Layout And Style
Quite Big
Decent - High Fps
Unique Gameplay
Phase: Beta

Inspiration:
This map was inspired by a friend's request for a gun game map based in a ruined city, apocolyptic style.  However after playing around with textures and layout I converted it to a 1800-1900's style.  This isn't a very explored theme within Css and especially not gun game.  Allowing me to create a unique realistic map.

In Development:
This map isn't finished it is currently in a beta phase after being tested and improved on the alpha version which was private.  Therefore people note any suggestions would help me to improve the map, I know it is quite big for a gungame map but I wished to create something different and unique to which I believe I have succeeded.  I am currently looking at developing a system to open different paths depending on the level of players.  As well as potentially making the map smaller so it works better but I need people to test it first and give their feedback.

	Check List: 1) 3d Skybox  2) Details

Also: All DECENT feedback is welcome :D

Thanks for interest in my map!

This map is derived from aim_map_usp and features elements of both aim_map_usp and gg_deagle5_4hm. The map is played during the sunrise while it is snowing across the map. There are ramps at each spawn, and boxes scattered around the center of the map to make it feel like your playing both usp and deagle at the same time. There is a basement with some explosive barrels to help keep people from camping down there, as well as a light so you can see. There is also a secret room in the map, there is only one teleporter to get in to it though. There are only images in the secret room, so it's pretty much pointless and doesn't really effect the gameplay at all.


I would appreciate if anybody decides to go about and edit the map to their liking or whatever to credit me as an author.


=CmG=|S| Knight (Kn1ght)


Also, for some reason, FPSBanana keeps checking background music as an effect, and knives on the ground even after unchecking them, so note that even though it says that, there is no background music or knives on the ground in this map.
